<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:52:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>实验药物通过修复肠道逆转严重脂肪肝疾病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/experimental-drug-reverses-severe-fatty-liver-disease-by-repairing-the-gut</link><description>密歇根医学院开发的一种实验药物在动物研究中显示出能够通过恢复肠道健康来逆转严重的脂肪肝疾病。研究结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/experimental-drug-reverses-severe-fatty-liver-disease-by-repairing-the-gut.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/experimental-drug-reverses-severe-fatty-liver-disease-by-repairing-the-gut</guid></item><item><title>合成旋转将黑洞能量理论带入实验室，放大波</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/synthetic-rotation-brings-black-hole-energy-theory-into-lab-amplifying-waves</link><description>半个多世纪前，罗杰·彭罗斯爵士设想了一种场景，可以从极速旋转的黑洞中提取能量。他提出，进入其能层（被旋转黑洞拖动的空间区域）的粒子可能会分裂成两部分。一部分可能落入黑洞，而另一部分则携带比原始粒子更多的能量逃脱。基于这一理论，物理学家雅科夫·泽尔多维奇后来预测，波与足够快的旋转物体相互作用可以从中提取能量并被放大。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/synthetic-rotation-brings-black-hole-energy-theory-into-lab-amplifying-waves.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:37:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/synthetic-rotation-brings-black-hole-energy-theory-into-lab-amplifying-waves</guid></item><item><title>研究口腔炎症性疾病如何帮助研究人员了解其他人类疾病</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-studying-oral-inflammatory-diseases-can-help-researchers-understand-other-human-diseases</link><description>来自 VCU 梅西综合癌症中心、VCU 牙科学院和宾夕法尼亚大学的研究小组最近发表了一项研究&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-studying-oral-inflammatory-diseases-can-help-researchers-understand-other-human-diseases.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/how-studying-oral-inflammatory-diseases-can-help-researchers-understand-other-human-diseases</guid></item><item><title>大卫·辛克莱博士：年龄逆转疗法的首次人体试验#podcast #lifespan #longevity</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dr-david-sinclair-the-first-human-trial-of-an-age-reversal-therapy-podcast-lifespan-longevity</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:07:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/dr-david-sinclair-the-first-human-trial-of-an-age-reversal-therapy-podcast-lifespan-longevity</guid></item><item><title>Senolytics 与干细胞的结合在小鼠身上显示出希望</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice</link><description>与 Immorta Bio 相关的一项新研究表明&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 01:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/combining-senolytics-and-stem-cells-shows-promise-in-mice</guid></item><item><title>物理学家终于构建了十多年前预测的量子材料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago</link><description>研究人员通过创造一种长期寻求的二维量子材料并确认其不寻常的导电边缘态，实现了一个重要的里程碑。通过应变控制这些状态的能力可能使该材料成为未来室温量子电子学的有前途的平台。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 01:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/physicists-finally-build-a-quantum-material-predicted-more-than-a-decade-ago</guid></item><item><title>AIE 网络研讨会 — 制作 Horsegirls</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls</link><description>与创作团队一起了解广受好评的独立电影《Horsegirls》的幕后故事，将这个非凡的故事变为现实。主持人德文·莫里西 (Devin Morrissey) 与编剧兼导演劳伦·梅耶林 (Lauren Meyering)、女主角莉莲·卡里尔 (Lillian Carrier)、制片人迈克尔·谢尔曼 (Michael Sherman)、麦肯齐·布里登 (Mackenzie Breeden) 和阿利克斯·马迪根-约金 (Alix Madigan-Yorkin)、自闭症敏感性协调员克洛伊·埃斯特尔 (Chloe Estelle) 一起就电影制作过程进行了精彩对话——从发展故事和创作真实的表演到制作、宣传和确保包容性的制作环境。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:57:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/aie-webinar-making-horsegirls</guid></item><item><title>人工智能教父：一个新物种正在出现——我们无法阻止它 |杰弗里·辛顿（诺贝尔奖）</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-godfather-of-ai-a-new-species-is-emerging-and-we-cant-stop-it-geoffrey-hinton-nobel</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-godfather-of-ai-a-new-species-is-emerging-and-we-cant-stop-it-geoffrey-hinton-nobel</guid></item><item><title>与其他生物不同</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/unlike-other-organisms</link><description>与其他生物体不同，水母水母可以如此迅速地修复损伤，您实际上可以在几分钟内看到小伤口闭合。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/marine-biological-laboratory-mblwoodshole-instagram-photos-and-videos.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/unlike-other-organisms</guid></item><item><title>SensorFM：迈向可穿戴健康数据的通用智能和接口</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data</link><description>我们推出了 SensorFM，这是一种可穿戴健康的基础模型，已根据来自 500 万人的超过 1 万亿分钟的传感器数据进行了预训练。通过共同缩放模型大小和数据，SensorFM 学习了人类生理学的通用表示，可转换为 35 个健康预测任务，支持标签高效适应和数据填充，并可以作为个人健康代理的基础工具。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 00:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/sensorfm-towards-a-general-intelligence-and-interface-for-wearable-health-data</guid></item></channel></rss>